function evaluateProperty({api : {state, data}, helpers}) {
  const pb = data.look_up_photobooths.results[0];

  return isSame("photoboothInstanceId", pb._row_data.uniqueValue) && 
    isSame("selectedCameraDeviceId", pb.camera_device_id.value) && 
    isSame("watermarkImage", pb.watermark_image.value) && 
    isSame("watermarkImagePosition", pb.watermark_image_position.value) && 
    isSame("watermarkImageHeight", pb.watermark_image_height.value) && 
    isSame("gap", pb.gap.value) && 
    isSame("fillStyle", pb.fill_style.value) && 
    isSame("chinHeight", pb.chin_height.value) && 
    isSame("photoboothLongName", pb.long_name.value);


  function isSame(statePropName, dbValue) {
    console.log("Is Same?", statePropName, `${state[statePropName]} == ${dbValue} =  ${state[statePropName] == dbValue}`);
    return state[statePropName] == dbValue;
  }
}]]></script><script_api_version>2.0.0</script_api_version><sys_class_name>sys_ux_client_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>jon.lind</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2023-04-04 20:29:47</sys_created_on><sys_id>5f9547f887c6651089790fe5dabb35ce</sys_id><sys_mod_count>4</sys_mod_count><sys_name>button_1/disabled</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Photobooth App" source="x_snc_pb_app">baa73cb74742dd10552caf52736d43f1</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Photobooth App">baa73cb74742dd10552caf52736d43f1</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ux_client_script_5f9547f887c6651089790fe5dabb35ce</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>jon.lind</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2023-04-04 20:44:53</sys_updated_on><target>macroponent</target><type>transform</type></sys_ux_client_script></record_update>
